{"title": "Declara\u00e7\u00e3o de 18 de Mar\u00e7o", "published time": "2024-03-19T20:45:00+08:00", "images": ["https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjC-f5XHyTfiARyI2tjZby3LDJ3xrlhaUKFUj9GsiArMI7xdIoA6hW0pi6kn9UeM5IVr7dxDNdDUngttcFMs1YHmmk9t-PDeJvUqtSWS45dN2v69cuo7ObWz4JjcKMSllgChDge0nLhw5Hhv_vdjo7C4lLH85Gv0blNIWStUlSqNv6r2FD1nji45CdaRCk/s1600/descarga.png"], "content": "<div class=\"post-body entry-content\" id=\"post-body-1756777851906925898\" itemprop=\"description articleBody\"><p></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjC-f5XHyTfiARyI2tjZby3LDJ3xrlhaUKFUj9GsiArMI7xdIoA6hW0pi6kn9UeM5IVr7dxDNdDUngttcFMs1YHmmk9t-PDeJvUqtSWS45dN2v69cuo7ObWz4JjcKMSllgChDge0nLhw5Hhv_vdjo7C4lLH85Gv0blNIWStUlSqNv6r2FD1nji45CdaRCk/s275/descarga.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><span><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"183\" data-original-width=\"275\" height=\"183\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-19T20-45-00-08-00/000000.png\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-19T20-45-00-08-00/000000.png\" width=\"275\"/></span></a></div><span><br/></span><p></p><p><span><em><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span>Prolet\u00e1rios de todos os pa\u00edses, uni-vos!</span></span></em></span></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><p><span></span></p><p><span><strong><span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">18 de mar\u00e7o</span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">\u2013 Dia de Solidariedade aos Presos Pol\u00edticos \u2013 homenagem</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Prisioneiros comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios!</span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">18 de mar\u00e7o \u00e9 o Dia Internacional de Solidariedade aos Presos Pol\u00edticos.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A Red Aid, fundada pelo Comintern em 1920, declarou o dia 18 de mar\u00e7o, dia da funda\u00e7\u00e3o da Comuna de Paris, como o \"Dia Internacional de Solidariedade aos Presos Pol\u00edticos\" em 1923 e o dedicou aos presos pol\u00edticos.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">No dia 18 de mar\u00e7o, ser\u00e1 expressa solidariedade aos presos pol\u00edticos de todo o mundo.</span></span></span></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Em todos os per\u00edodos da hist\u00f3ria houve grande resist\u00eancia aos sistemas de explora\u00e7\u00e3o e opress\u00e3o em que vivemos por quil\u00f4metros de anos, e um alto pre\u00e7o foi pago por isso.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A toda luta contra os sistemas dominantes de explora\u00e7\u00e3o e opress\u00e3o, a toda resist\u00eancia, a rea\u00e7\u00e3o das classes dominantes tem sido semelhante: destruir todos os movimentos que se dirigem contra sua exist\u00eancia para garantir sua exist\u00eancia e, sobretudo, aqueles que est\u00e3o no poder de destruir aqueles que foram submetidos a elas.</span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">liderar este. movimento.</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Pela ira que foi lan\u00e7ada contra a ordem vigente,</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">o</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">impulso</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">que surge</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">do</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">desejo e esfor\u00e7os para mudar a ordem vigente,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Eles s\u00f3 podem estar indo na dire\u00e7\u00e3o certa sob uma lideran\u00e7a adequada.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">\u00c9 por isso que as classes dominantes querem destruir aqueles que canalizam a raiva e o desejo de mudan\u00e7a do povo, e isolar do povo aqueles que n\u00e3o podem ser destru\u00eddos.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A outra dimens\u00e3o da intoler\u00e2ncia e agress\u00e3o das classes dominantes contra os movimentos populares revolucion\u00e1rios, comunistas e democr\u00e1ticos \u00e9 garantir que as massas oprimidas permane\u00e7am em sil\u00eancio e n\u00e3o ousem se rebelar.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Matando e oprimindo campe\u00f5es</span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">do povo, as classes dominantes enviam um recado \u00e0s massas oprimidas: \"Se voc\u00eas se op\u00f5em a n\u00f3s, faremos o mesmo com voc\u00eas\".</span></span></span></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">\"</span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Os fil\u00f3sofos apenas interpretaram o mundo de forma diferente;</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O que importa</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">\u00c9</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">mud\u00e1-los.\"</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">disse Karl Marx, o grande mestre do proletariado.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios lutam</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Para a realiza\u00e7\u00e3o desse ideal, para isso s\u00e3o mortos, presos por isso.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Repetidas vezes, prisioneiros comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios em centros de tortura e pris\u00f5es mostraram</span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">que, enquanto a vida continua, grandes exemplos podem ser dados da continua\u00e7\u00e3o da luta de classes sob qualquer condi\u00e7\u00e3o de vida.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O caminho exige assumir esses riscos, e \u00e9 com essa consci\u00eancia que comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios lutam contra os sistemas de explora\u00e7\u00e3o vigentes.</span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O corpo de cada comunista e revolucion\u00e1rio assassinado, cada tempo passado na pris\u00e3o, tamb\u00e9m lan\u00e7a as bases para a constru\u00e7\u00e3o da sociedade do futuro.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A burguesia e seus lacaios querem garantir a rendi\u00e7\u00e3o submetendo \u00e0s condi\u00e7\u00f5es mais violentas aqueles que n\u00e3o podem ser massacrados nas pris\u00f5es.</span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">prisioneiros comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Por sua vez</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">, n\u00e3o hesitam em transformar as pris\u00f5es, onde o inimigo se sente mais forte, em palco de luta de classes.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Portanto, n\u00e3o devemos definir como v\u00edtimas os prisioneiros comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios nas pris\u00f5es.</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Pelo contr\u00e1rio, devemos</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">defini-los como justos</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">e</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">este</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">cumprimentar</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios s\u00e3o mortos, presos e torturados n\u00e3o apenas porque t\u00eam ideias diferentes sobre os sistemas de explora\u00e7\u00e3o existentes, mas tamb\u00e9m porque fazem algo para mudar essas ideias, para organizar e unir o povo.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Trata-se, antes de tudo, de uma guerra ideol\u00f3gica, encarnada por dois</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">classes hostis e mutuamente incompat\u00edveis.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O assassinato e a pris\u00e3o de comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios n\u00e3o resolve o problema da burguesia, pois as condi\u00e7\u00f5es objetivas do sistema imperialista sustentam que a burguesia ainda est\u00e1 no poder.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">e apresentar a contradi\u00e7\u00e3o entre opressores e oprimidos.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A situa\u00e7\u00e3o objectiva existente, o</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Contradi\u00e7\u00f5es cada vez mais profundas se refletem diretamente nas contradi\u00e7\u00f5es de classe</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">e o vazio deixado pelos revolucion\u00e1rios e comunistas assassinados e presos \u00e9 preenchido com novos.</span></span></span></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Em</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">em que medida as contradi\u00e7\u00f5es do sistema dominante se aprofundam e</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Os becos sem sa\u00edda em que ele cai se multiplicam,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Na medida em que cresce o medo do \"coveiro\", as classes dominantes n\u00e3o hesitam em se tornar cada vez mais</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Concreto</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">para revelar sua verdadeira identidade.</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">rosto.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ao mesmo tempo, a crise cada vez mais profunda e n\u00e3o resolvida do sistema est\u00e1 se movendo</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">\u00e0 burguesia e \u00e0s classes dominantes exploradoras de todos os tipos</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">centralizar ainda mais o mecanismo do Estado soberano,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">tanto com leis quanto com organiza\u00e7\u00f5es de fato,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Voc\u00ea</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Continuar a progredir no</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Instrumentos.</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">de opress\u00e3o</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Nos pa\u00edses capitalistas-imperialistas</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">que se autodenominam democracias \"ideais\" e \"progressistas\",</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">As sucessivas leis de seguran\u00e7a, as novas leis que ampliam o poder dos \u00f3rg\u00e3os repressivos do Estado, nos mostram</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ou seja, que a burguesia tem a capacidade de... Usar a \"m\u00e1scara da democracia\" perdeu.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A burguesia est\u00e1 se restabelecendo</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">sua posi\u00e7\u00e3o contra a classe trabalhadora, contra os trabalhadores oprimidos e os povos oprimidos, com todos os</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">dele</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Reacionarismo</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Nos pa\u00edses coloniais e semicoloniais dominados pelo imperialismo,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Os esquemas usuais s\u00e3o</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">formas de governo parlamentar e extraparlamentar com diferentes</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Tons de fascismo e rea\u00e7\u00e3o.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Nesses pa\u00edses, todos os membros da oposi\u00e7\u00e3o, a come\u00e7ar pelos comunistas e revolucion\u00e1rios, est\u00e3o expostos ao terrorismo de Estado sistem\u00e1tico e permanente.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A profundidade da contradi\u00e7\u00e3o entre as classes dominantes e o</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Povos</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Opresso</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">em</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Esses pa\u00edses determinam a intensidade da luta de classes.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Para as classes dominantes,</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Que</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Eles s\u00f3 podem manter a escravid\u00e3o do imperialismo atrav\u00e9s de um regime de terror irrestrito, o terrorismo de Estado \u00e9 mais uma necessidade do que uma op\u00e7\u00e3o.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">As leis s\u00e3o apenas uma fachada para o fascismo, a rea\u00e7\u00e3o e o terrorismo de Estado.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">As pris\u00f5es, por sua vez, s\u00e3o instrumentos de tortura e opress\u00e3o.</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">O</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">As classes dominantes da Turquia, \u00cdndia, Filipinas, Peru, Ir\u00e3, Israel, etc. est\u00e3o aprofundando seu controle sobre o</span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">isolamento, que eles usam</span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">de todas as formas poss\u00edveis</span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">manter os presos na pris\u00e3o.</span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Est\u00e1 impedido</span></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">o tratamento de prisioneiros gravemente doentes sob v\u00e1rios pretextos;</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"></span></span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\"><span style=\"verti